OL,6,FHe also rejected claims that the
OL,7,Fpackage altered domestic laws enabling
OL,8,Fthe application of EU laws in Northern
OL,9,FIreland and he found that the region
OL,10,Fwould continue to be treated as an EU
OL,11,Fterritory when it came to certain
OL,12,Ftrading rules.
