OL,6,FMr Allister and Mr Bryson were at
OL,7,FParliament Buildings at Stormont on
OL,8,FFriday to give their reaction to Mr
OL,9,FLarkin's findings.
OL,11,FThe TUV leader said the opinion
OL,12,Fundermined the "spin" that has
OL,13,Faccompanied the Government deal which
OL,14,Fhas convinced the DUP to return to
OL,15,Fdevolution.
