OL,3,CStormont deal has not removed Irish
OL,4,CSea border, says ex-attorney general
OL,6,F"We arrive at a situation where,
OL,7,Fdespite all the spin, and all the
OL,8,Fhype, and all the pretence, and all
OL,9,Fthe false claims about restoring our
OL,10,Fplace within the United Kingdom, and
OL,11,Fthe removal of the Irish Sea (border),
OL,12,Fwhen you apply the key legal analysis
OL,13,Fof this matter, then it doesn't stand
OL,14,Fup," he said.
OL,16,FMr Allister warned that the existing
OL,17,Fpost-Brexit arrangements would attempt
OL,18,Fto deliver a united Ireland by stealth.
